metadata.name: First gm Spoken
metadata.description:
First gm spoken – will it ever be found?

A gm enthusiast builds a time machine and travels to the past to find out "the first spoken gm"! He finds that web3 inhabitants have devolved into two sides: the gm sayers and the good morning sayers. His machine suddenly disappears, so he explores the past and forgotten pre-punk gothic world. After narrowly escaping capture by the good morning sayers, the gm enthusiast recovers his machine and journeys further forward to the world’s end. The gm enthusiast plants the seed of a future where WAGMI & grounds those ideas in the principles & theories of Seizing The Memes Of Production. „There is intelligence where there is change“, he said, „so lets bring this change to every corner of web3 & gm together!“ tbc...

A wildalps x peterart18 mixed media collab.
